quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  27,67,Kafiron ney kaha kay kiya jab hum mitti ho jayen gay aur humaray baap dada bhi kiya hum phir nikalay jayen gay
  27,68,Hum aur humaray baap dadon ko boht pehlay say yeh waday diye jatay rahey. Kuch nahi yeh to sirf aglon kay afsaney hain
  27,69,Keh dijiye kay zamin mein chal phir ker zara dekho to sahi kay gunehgaron ka kaisa anjam hua
  27,70,Aap inn kay baray mein ghum na keren aur inn kay dao ghaat say tang dil na hon
  27,71,Kehtay hain kay yeh wada kab hai agar sachay ho to batla do
  27,72,Jawab dijiye! kay shayad baaz woh cheezen jin ki tum jaldi macha rahey ho tum say boht hi qareen hogaee hon
  27,73,Yaqeenan aap ka perwerdigar tamam logon per baray hi fazal wala hai lekin aksar log na-shukri kertay hain
  27,74,Be-shak aap ka rab unn cheezon ko bhi janta hai jinhen unn kay seenay chupa rahey hain aur jinhen zahir ker rahey hain
  27,75,Aasman-o-zamin ki koi posheeda cheez bhi aisi nahi jo roshan aur khulli kitab mein na ho
  27,76,Yaqeena yeh quran bani israeel kay samney unn aksar cheezon ka biyan ker raha hai jin mein yeh ikhtilaf kertay hain
  27,77,Aur yeh quran eman walon kay liye yaqeenan hidayat aur rehmat hai
  27,78,Aap ka rab unn kay darmiyan apnay hukum say sab faislay ker dey ga woh bara hi ghalib aur dana hai
  27,79,Pus aap yaqeenan Allah hi per bharosa rakhiye yaqeenan aap sachay aur khullay deen per hain
  27,80,Be-shak aap murdon ko nahi suna saktay hain aur na behron ko apni pukar suna saktay hain jabkay woh peeth pheray roo gardaan ja rahey hon
  27,81,Aur na aap andhon ko unn ki gumrahee say hata ker rehnumaee ker saktay hain aap to sirf unhen suna saktay hain jo humari aayaton per eman laye hain phir woh farmanbardaar ho jatay hain
  27,82,Jab unn kay upper azab ka wada sabit hojaye ga hum zamin say unn kay liye aik janwar nikalen gay jo unn say batein kerta hoga kay log humari aayaton per yaqeen nahi kertay thay